Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科選手 竟然領先乾選手兩分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但 乾選手也不惶多讓地飛往了第三浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}切換的反應速度真不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到第三飛行線進行抄截
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分 二比一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒問題的 沙希 剛才被拿走的分 就在第三飛行線回收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}接下來輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}勉強能躲得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}和之前比賽時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她在享受?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是瘋狂特訓的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}三對一的練習 她可是練了很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科選手 面對乾選手的猛攻 都巧妙的躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}很好 明日香 別大意囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fnDFGPOP1-W3\fs60}咲{\r\blur2} 小真白 小{\fnDFGPOP1-W3\fs60}窓{\r\blur2}果 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小莉佳 佐藤院同學 真藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還有...各務老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}全部 都被躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}大家的希望 就由我來回應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}超級Low Yo Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科 得分 三比一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}拿下啦 倉科選手拿下第三分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽時間還剩三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香只要再撐三分鐘就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 解放平衡器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 第一階段 50%解...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.36,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}解放100%吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}亞格拉賓 第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(825,975)}{\blur2}Agravain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}平衡器 完全解放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 讓所有人都沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}調整了反重力鞋的平衡器嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 是把它完全關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啟動狀態下能把它關掉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}艾瓦隆...幾年前突然竄出來的品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒想到竟然開發出了那種技術嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}本來 如果把作為安全裝置的平衡器關掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就會變得在空中無法維持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但只要能駕馭它 就能夠引出反重力鞋的最大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}竟然能駕馭得如此完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來她有著超乎常人的體力和感官能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 用超音噴射拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(975,975)}{\blur2}Sonic Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就這樣飛去搶浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分 三比三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣就...同分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}接下來做的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}綠光閃擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}讓大家見識一下妳的美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這...這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個動作是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不管怎麼做都好 快甩開她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒用的 這是艾瓦隆和我們所構築出來的完美世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}覆蓋著會場的這片沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這就是艾瓦隆的祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(960,975)}{\blur2}Game Set
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}由於雙方同分 在十分鐘的休息後 將進行延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好啦 同分後的延長賽 就是我們FC的最終樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}機會難得 所以我準備了謝幕的特別演出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無能為力 只能被壓著打的那五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一定會既寧靜又美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那雙叫亞格拉賓的反重力鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(900,975)}{\blur2}Agravain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在比賽中也能夠自由調整平衡器和引動率嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 能夠自由駕馭那雙反重力鞋的 乾同學自身的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哦 真藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}擁有絕對王者名號的你也要投降了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就現階段而言 雖然很令人不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得...倉科同學...也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學...沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她的實力至今仍是未知數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得她還有著莫大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她一定能讓我們看到更有趣的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}表現得很好 沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那邊看起來好像很有問題的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個樣子 看來是撐不過延長賽那五分鐘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}再多飛一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想和她再一起多飛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香學姊 妳還有HP嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害啊 關掉平衡器竟然還能做出那樣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學 越飛越高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真快樂啊 這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也要關掉平衡器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}太有勇無謀了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳之前試的時候 不是連飛都沒辦法好好飛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}而且 妳的反重力鞋和艾瓦隆不同 沒辦法在空中進行切換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一旦關掉 就無法復原了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}即使如此 妳還是要關嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不想就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想再和乾同學一起多飛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請讓我關掉吧 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就算會化成灰也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有關係啦 妳又不是傑菲利翁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是 說不定妳能成為天空的霸者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂 連美{\fnDFGPOP1-W3\fs60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊都...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也 就相信明日香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香的話一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 我也把一切都託付給明日香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也託付給妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}拜託妳囉 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也是 倉科
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}您感覺到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們的FC 完美的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個時候也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在那美麗之中載浮載沉的 透徹人心的沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那只不過是恐懼而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雙方選手互相切磋 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}讓彼此互相產生快樂 這就是名為Flying Circus的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如果目的只是壓倒對手並取得勝利的話 就不會取Circus這名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在這場延長賽過後 您是否還能說出一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}現在 即將進行決賽的延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好啦 接下來要進行本大賽有史以來第一次的延長賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}延長賽限時五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如果還是沒能決出勝負 將由先馳得點的人獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你們沒有逃跑呢 對於那份勇氣 我就稱讚你們一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學 這次我們一起飛到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(960,975)}{\blur2}Set
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是的 看來連往前飛的體力都沒有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反重力鞋的翅膀...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}難道說 妳把平衡器...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為了和乾同學妳一起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼會...妳怎麼可能駕馭得了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她成功駕馭它了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就這樣飛去第三飛行線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}除了厲害 真的不知道該怎麼形容了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 快追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 去抄截
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科 得分 五比三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害 太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒想到倉科選手成功解放平衡器 現在領先乾選手兩分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}行得通喔 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的變成一場不得了的比賽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣 FC的世界又要改變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}選手們要從平衡器中解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}新時代要來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}再次用綠光閃擊封住她的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是怎麼了? 是和那時候一樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}全身都燃燒起來的 這份感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳不享受嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}享受...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 我要先上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分 五比四
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學的表情變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總覺得變得好有生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科 得分 六比四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小明日香 好快樂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學 再繼續飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希竟然會在比賽中露出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分 六比五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾 得分 六比六
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好啦 終於同分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}延長賽的所剩時間也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真華麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊 我都著迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她們兩人的軌跡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如此...如此不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她們不過是在互相追逐 互相競爭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但為什麼...會如此地美麗呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}被眼前的絕景震懾到我都忘記轉播了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}五分鐘的延長賽早就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}接下來 誰先獲得一分就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}控制...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}背後要被碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科選手得分 七比六 倉科選手勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小...小美{\fnDFGPOP1-W3\fs60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼嘛 這不是贏了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是優勝喔 恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}優勝...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}等...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科 謝謝妳實現了我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.66,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}老哥 你太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是場愉快的比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們一直希望能被憧憬著的您認同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是 我們錯了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒那回事 我也一直都覺得我犯了個錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但後來我了解到 那個錯誤 對FC的成長也是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因而釋懷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...好像有點了解Circus的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Flying Circus是令人快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是能鼓舞人心的運動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這場比賽 妳快樂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 雖然有點不甘心
